#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.date_range.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.date\\_range"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:1 of
msgid "Return a fixed frequency DatetimeIndex."
msgstr "返回一个固定频率的 DatetimeIndex。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.date_range.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:3 of
msgid "Left bound for generating dates."
msgstr "生成日期的左边界。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:5 of
msgid "Right bound for generating dates."
msgstr "生成日期的右边界。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:7 of
msgid "Number of periods to generate."
msgstr "要生成的周期数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:9 of
msgid ""
"Frequency strings can have multiples, e.g. '5H'. See :ref:`here "
"<timeseries.offset_aliases>` for a list of frequency aliases."
msgstr ""
"频率字符串可以有倍数，例如 '5H'。请参见 :ref:`此处 <timeseries.offset_"
"aliases>` 获取频率别名列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:13 of
msgid ""
"Time zone name for returning localized DatetimeIndex, for example "
"'Asia/Hong_Kong'. By default, the resulting DatetimeIndex is timezone-"
"naive."
msgstr ""
"用于返回本地化 DatetimeIndex 的时区名称，例如 'Asia/Hong_Kong'。默认情况"
"下，结果 DatetimeIndex 是非时区感知的。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:17 of
msgid "Normalize start/end dates to midnight before generating date range."
msgstr "在生成日期范围之前将起始/结束日期规范化到午夜。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:19 of
msgid "Name of the resulting DatetimeIndex."
msgstr "结果 DatetimeIndex 的名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:21 of
msgid "Include boundaries; Whether to set each bound as closed or open."
msgstr "包含边界；是否将每个边界设置为闭合或开放。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:23 of
msgid "For compatibility. Has no effect on the result."
msgstr "用于兼容性。对结果没有影响。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.date_range.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:25 of
msgid "**rng**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.date_range.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DatetimeIndex`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:31 of
msgid "An immutable container for datetimes."
msgstr "一个用于日期时间的不可变容器。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`timedelta_range`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:34 of
msgid "Return a fixed frequency TimedeltaIndex."
msgstr "返回一个固定频率的 TimedeltaIndex。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:36 of
msgid ":py:obj:`period_range`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:37 of
msgid "Return a fixed frequency PeriodIndex."
msgstr "返回一个固定频率的 PeriodIndex。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:39 of
msgid ":py:obj:`interval_range`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:40 of
msgid "Return a fixed frequency IntervalIndex."
msgstr "返回一个固定频率的 IntervalIndex。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:43 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:44 of
msgid ""
"Of the four parameters ``start``, ``end``, ``periods``, and ``freq``, "
"exactly three must be specified. If ``freq`` is omitted, the resulting "
"``DatetimeIndex`` will have ``periods`` linearly spaced elements between "
"``start`` and ``end`` (closed on both sides)."
msgstr ""
"在 ``start``、``end``、``periods`` 和 ``freq`` 这四个参数中，必须指定其中"
"三个。如果省略 ``freq``，则结果 ``DatetimeIndex`` 将在 ``start`` 和 ``end"
"`` 之间具有 ``periods`` 个线性分布的元素（两端闭合）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:49 of
msgid ""
"To learn more about the frequency strings, please see `this link "
"<https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/user_guide/timeseries.html"
"#offset-aliases>`__."
msgstr ""
"要了解更多关于频率字符串的信息，请参见 `此链接 <https://pandas.pydata.org"
"/pandas-docs/stable/user_guide/timeseries.html#offset-aliases>`__。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:53 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:54 of
msgid "**Specifying the values**"
msgstr "**指定值**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:56 of
msgid ""
"The next four examples generate the same `DatetimeIndex`, but vary the "
"combination of `start`, `end` and `periods`."
msgstr ""
"接下来的四个示例生成相同的 `DatetimeIndex`，但 `start`、`end` 和 `periods"
"` 的组合各不相同。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:59 of
msgid ""
"Specify `start` and `end`, with the default daily frequency. >>> import "
"maxframe.dataframe as md"
msgstr ""
"指定 `start` 和 `end`，使用默认的日频率。>>> import maxframe.dataframe as"
" md"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:67 of
msgid "Specify `start` and `periods`, the number of periods (days)."
msgstr "指定 `start` 和 `periods`，表示周期数（天数）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:74 of
msgid "Specify `end` and `periods`, the number of periods (days)."
msgstr "指定 `end` 和 `periods`，表示周期数（天数）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:81 of
msgid ""
"Specify `start`, `end`, and `periods`; the frequency is generated "
"automatically (linearly spaced)."
msgstr "指定 `start`、`end` 和 `periods`；频率会自动生成（线性间隔）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:89 of
msgid "**Other Parameters**"
msgstr "**其他参数**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:91 of
msgid "Changed the `freq` (frequency) to ``'M'`` (month end frequency)."
msgstr "将 `freq`（频率）更改为 ``'M'``（月末频率）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:98 of
msgid "Multiples are allowed"
msgstr "允许多倍数"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:105 of
msgid "`freq` can also be specified as an Offset object."
msgstr "`freq` 也可以指定为 Offset 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:112 of
msgid "Specify `tz` to set the timezone."
msgstr "指定 `tz` 来设置时区。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:120 of
msgid ""
"`inclusive` controls whether to include `start` and `end` that are on the"
" boundary. The default, \"both\", includes boundary points on either end."
msgstr ""
"`inclusive` 控制是否包含位于边界上的 `start` 和 `end`。默认值 \"both\" "
"表示包含两端的边界点。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:127 of
msgid "Use ``inclusive='left'`` to exclude `end` if it falls on the boundary."
msgstr "使用 ``inclusive='left'`` 可在 `end` 落在边界上时将其排除。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:133 of
msgid ""
"Use ``inclusive='right'`` to exclude `start` if it falls on the boundary,"
" and similarly inclusive='neither' will exclude both `start` and `end`."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``inclusive='right'`` 可在 `start` 落在边界上时将其排除，类似地，"
"inclusive='neither' 将同时排除 `start` 和 `end`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.date_range.date_range:141 of
msgid ""
"Pandas 1.4.0 or later is required to use ``inclusive='neither'``. "
"Otherwise an error may be raised."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``inclusive='neither'`` 需要 Pandas 1.4.0 或更高版本。否则可能会引发"
"错误。"

